" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女下男上張腿當打椿機咁屌 最好屌一下啲淫水擠一大堆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從佢背後用手托開對淫腳令佢正面咁屌 等佢自己睇睇下啲淫水幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中出之餘一定要射到佢成身都係精 再用有殘餘精液嘅大龜頭拍佢臉+磨嘴唇<br />\n最後塞入口等佢舔乾淨 令佢變成性奴液便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822fd78bc852465cf25c47e2837b95c8925ce65f","tid":827074,"uid":59595,"like":53,"dislike":4,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"2f4d6ec1c793dc652e0741e5d829c9608e9510ad","tid":827074,"uid":3893,"like":80,"dislike":17,"score":63,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:11:34.000Z","msg":"莊端兒咁撚樣衰  又大份  真係零興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T20:13:53.000Z","msg":"你呢d亞洲仔細份姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60e223e29e345bc3dbf577abd882243b940006d","tid":827074,"uid":135866,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"2f4d6ec1c793dc652e0741e5d829c9608e9510ad","tid":827074,"uid":3893,"like":80,"dislike":17,"score":63,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:11:34.000Z","msg":"莊端兒咁撚樣衰  又大份  真係零興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T20:15:28.000Z","msg":"矮仔唔識食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cf047ddda6733558bbb1a52782afe73cd76836","tid":827074,"uid":16201,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"676c6ac8400912d72d4f3b9fbc7413a94396fb5c","tid":827074,"uid":27920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2954f228453e07debbdb1afdaa6b10fdbab0745","tid":827074,"uid":164591,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"quote":{"pid":"a55dd3dbcd339653a9d49d6a70e312e41a78b6c1","tid":827074,"uid":144466,"like":213,"dislike":9,"scor